1
00:00:00,370 --> 00:00:01,770
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,770 --> 00:00:03,440
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,510 --> 00:00:05,310
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:06,950 --> 00:00:07,950
It was a person.

5
00:00:08,650 --> 00:00:10,150
Someone secretive...

6
00:00:10,420 --> 00:00:12,720
who could build something dangerous.

7
00:00:14,820 --> 00:00:17,720
A device was needed
to blow up and incinerate a car.

8
00:00:20,930 --> 00:00:22,360
What Park Tae Ho wanted...

9
00:00:23,660 --> 00:00:24,700
was a bomb maker!

10
00:00:31,270 --> 00:00:32,270
Do you get it now?

11
00:00:33,670 --> 00:00:35,310
No matter
how high and mighty you act,

12
00:00:36,340 --> 00:00:38,840
you've lived as a murderer's woman,
reeking of blood.

13
00:00:39,040 --> 00:00:40,510
Just like me.

14
00:00:43,620 --> 00:00:46,820
Exactly.
I knew you'd make that face.

15
00:00:47,750 --> 00:00:49,950
Kim Myung Hui, someone like you...

16
00:00:50,220 --> 00:00:52,420
could never stomach
a real killer like Park Tae Ho.

17
00:00:54,430 --> 00:00:56,660
Only someone like me can handle him.

18
00:00:56,660 --> 00:00:57,860
But you?

19
00:00:58,900 --> 00:01:01,330
You'd be too disgusted
to even stand being around him.

20
00:01:02,300 --> 00:01:03,300
But...

21
00:01:04,600 --> 00:01:07,010
do you know
what's even more disgusting than him?

22
00:01:09,110 --> 00:01:11,010
That's right. It's you.

23
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:15,750
Even though you know the truth,
you can't go against him.

24
00:01:16,850 --> 00:01:19,780
You need that man
to get your hands on Adele Group.

25
00:01:20,790 --> 00:01:24,060
You can't give up on Adele
after wanting it for 30 years.

26
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:28,260
To satisfy your greed,
you must throw yourself in his arms.

27
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,560
In the end,

28
00:01:32,700 --> 00:01:35,130
you'll die, disgusted...

29
00:01:36,530 --> 00:01:37,870
with Park Tae Ho...

30
00:01:38,900 --> 00:01:39,940
and with yourself.

31
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:02,360
You...

32
00:02:03,030 --> 00:02:04,300
It's really you.

33
00:02:05,660 --> 00:02:06,660
Baek Jin Ju.

34
00:02:08,630 --> 00:02:10,640
Hyun Jun,
did you do this on purpose?

35
00:02:11,700 --> 00:02:14,640
Don't tell me you're questioning
who I am.

36
00:02:20,180 --> 00:02:22,650
I'm done with dessert,
and you still haven't answered me.

37
00:02:24,180 --> 00:02:25,180
So I'll be leaving now.

38
00:02:27,020 --> 00:02:28,350
If you have feelings for me,

39
00:02:29,550 --> 00:02:31,190
just let me use you.

40
00:02:33,090 --> 00:02:34,290
Then at least...

41
00:02:35,130 --> 00:02:37,100
you get to have me by your side.

42
00:03:18,940 --> 00:03:20,670
If I let you use me...

43
00:03:21,140 --> 00:03:22,940
and keep you by my side,

44
00:03:26,510 --> 00:03:27,610
will you someday...

45
00:03:31,150 --> 00:03:32,650
come to love me?

46
00:03:35,820 --> 00:03:37,260
It's like I said before.

47
00:03:43,430 --> 00:03:44,660
I'll try.

48
00:03:58,140 --> 00:04:00,010
Once again, you chose to be honest.

49
00:04:03,010 --> 00:04:04,920
Have you never once lied to me?

50
00:04:07,050 --> 00:04:09,020
If there's anything you want
to come clean about,

51
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:11,020
now's the time.

52
00:04:11,590 --> 00:04:14,160
No. There's nothing.

53
00:04:18,030 --> 00:04:19,030
Really?

54
00:04:21,030 --> 00:04:23,030
Well, I have something to confess.

55
00:04:33,810 --> 00:04:35,410
The cake we ate today.

56
00:04:40,020 --> 00:04:41,290
Apparently,
they left out the chestnuts.

57
00:04:43,490 --> 00:04:45,290
Something about them
being out of season.

58
00:04:46,590 --> 00:04:47,590
Bummer, isn't it?

59
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,400
About my answer...

60
00:04:54,430 --> 00:04:56,230
Give me a little more time. You see,

61
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,740
I suddenly have a lot more
to think about.

62
00:05:27,330 --> 00:05:28,800
You're no different.

63
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:32,670
So stop acting all high and mighty
in front of me.

64
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:35,640
You can't even touch Park Tae Ho,
the murderer,

65
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:39,140
so don't get smart
and think you can come after me.

66
00:05:40,950 --> 00:05:44,080
While disgusted with yourself
in his arms,

67
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:48,550
while facing your reflection
as you claw your way to get Adele,

68
00:05:50,290 --> 00:05:51,320
die a little inside...

69
00:05:52,790 --> 00:05:53,790
every day.

70
00:06:01,930 --> 00:06:02,930
Maybe so.

71
00:06:04,940 --> 00:06:06,600
I might die inside.

72
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:10,440
But...

73
00:06:12,780 --> 00:06:14,280
even if I die a thousand deaths,

74
00:06:16,650 --> 00:06:19,350
I'll come back into your life.

75
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:28,560
Because...

76
00:06:30,030 --> 00:06:31,800
I'll come back like I did before.

77
00:06:34,900 --> 00:06:36,300
But this time,

78
00:06:38,740 --> 00:06:40,570
I'm going to live as you.

79
00:06:43,910 --> 00:06:46,380
What do you mean by that?

80
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:48,210
Live as me?

81
00:06:49,110 --> 00:06:52,620
Are you saying you'll replace me
as the chairman's wife?

82
00:06:55,220 --> 00:06:56,620
Would I even need to go that far?

83
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,990
Just watch how I become you,

84
00:07:04,860 --> 00:07:06,530
how I die...

85
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,700
and how I take your place.

86
00:07:10,540 --> 00:07:11,840
Watch in silence.

87
00:07:13,540 --> 00:07:14,570
In silence?

88
00:07:15,770 --> 00:07:17,740
You think I'm going to stand by
and let that happen?

89
00:07:17,740 --> 00:07:18,740
You'd better.

90
00:07:20,810 --> 00:07:22,580
Because if Chairman Park finds out,

91
00:07:23,080 --> 00:07:25,220
you'll be in even bigger trouble.

92
00:07:37,130 --> 00:07:38,530
How dare you threaten me?

93
00:07:39,130 --> 00:07:41,100
You think I'll even bat an eye?

94
00:08:08,260 --> 00:08:10,060
More than ever, it must feel like...

95
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,830
going home to the devil.

96
00:08:15,100 --> 00:08:16,770
In there, you have to face...

97
00:08:17,940 --> 00:08:19,800
that murderer, Park Tae Ho.

98
00:08:21,940 --> 00:08:24,710
How can you stand it,
pretending like everything is fine?

99
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:29,080
I've been...

100
00:08:30,650 --> 00:08:32,480
with the Adele family...

101
00:08:33,620 --> 00:08:34,920
for 30 years now, right?

102
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:37,790
That's right.

103
00:08:40,260 --> 00:08:41,630
From now on,

104
00:08:42,990 --> 00:08:45,500
I might have to throw away
those 30 years.

105
00:08:52,770 --> 00:08:53,770
I really...

106
00:08:54,570 --> 00:08:56,710
don't want to go back home
to him today.

107
00:09:01,380 --> 00:09:02,380
Then don't.

108
00:09:03,710 --> 00:09:05,180
Let's just get away for a day.

109
00:09:06,880 --> 00:09:08,920
Away from this wretched family.

110
00:09:20,060 --> 00:09:22,200
What? She's not coming home?

111
00:09:22,870 --> 00:09:25,700
She's staying out all night? Why?

112
00:09:27,170 --> 00:09:28,510
I didn't ask.

113
00:09:28,910 --> 00:09:32,310
If that's what she decided,
she must have her reasons.

114
00:09:33,910 --> 00:09:36,910
Don't tell me it's because
of your wedding.

115
00:09:38,180 --> 00:09:42,690
If this is her way of protesting,
tell her it's useless.

116
00:09:43,850 --> 00:09:45,920
Tell her
if she continues to defy me,

117
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:48,590
she'll lose her position
as president,

118
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:50,800
and even Adele itself.

119
00:09:50,800 --> 00:09:53,330
Don't you care
if you lose Mother over this?

120
00:09:55,570 --> 00:09:56,570
What?

121
00:09:56,570 --> 00:09:59,100
Do you think it's easy
holding out in this family?

122
00:09:59,470 --> 00:10:02,370
How will you make her stay
if she gives up on you?

123
00:10:04,110 --> 00:10:06,180
If you want her to come home,

124
00:10:06,410 --> 00:10:08,280
just leave her be
for at least a day.

125
00:10:23,430 --> 00:10:24,430
Manager Kang.

126
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:27,200
Track Myung Hui's movements
and report back to me immediately.

127
00:10:28,030 --> 00:10:31,070
Where she goes, who she meets,
and what she does.

128
00:10:31,070 --> 00:10:32,470
I want to know everything.

129
00:10:32,700 --> 00:10:33,700
Right now!

130
00:10:40,580 --> 00:10:42,050
She'd give up Adele?

131
00:10:44,820 --> 00:10:46,250
And I'd lose her?

132
00:11:19,350 --> 00:11:21,520
- Hello?
- It's me.

133
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:22,890
Is Mother all right?

134
00:11:22,950 --> 00:11:23,950
Yes.

135
00:11:24,220 --> 00:11:27,730
She just fell asleep.
Everything go smoothly on your end?

136
00:11:27,890 --> 00:11:30,490
Yes, I spoke with the chairman.

137
00:11:31,300 --> 00:11:32,760
He was upset,

138
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,770
but it won't be a big problem.

139
00:11:36,130 --> 00:11:37,270
That's a relief.

140
00:11:38,270 --> 00:11:39,270
By the way,

141
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:42,070
why aren't you asking what's wrong?

142
00:11:43,170 --> 00:11:46,710
I figured it'd be harder on her
if I asked,

143
00:11:47,340 --> 00:11:49,880
especially since I already
upset her last time.

144
00:11:51,250 --> 00:11:55,150
Please take good care of her.
Call me if anything happens.

145
00:11:56,290 --> 00:11:58,090
Yes, of course.

146
00:12:01,290 --> 00:12:02,490
Our Min Jun...

147
00:12:03,160 --> 00:12:05,430
He's really all grown up now.

148
00:12:06,230 --> 00:12:08,700
For a decent man like him
to have a murderer for a father...

149
00:12:10,100 --> 00:12:13,670
And the person he killed
was someone Min Jun cared about.

150
00:12:15,670 --> 00:12:17,480
When Min Jun finds out the truth,

151
00:12:19,180 --> 00:12:20,210
he'll be...

152
00:12:33,520 --> 00:12:35,190
You didn't show up for work today.

153
00:12:35,590 --> 00:12:36,590
I just...

154
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:38,630
didn't feel like it.

155
00:12:41,070 --> 00:12:42,070
Baek Jin Ju.

156
00:12:45,670 --> 00:12:46,740
What if by some miracle,

157
00:12:47,910 --> 00:12:49,470
Baek Jin Ju were still alive,

158
00:12:51,010 --> 00:12:52,180
how would you feel?

159
00:12:54,180 --> 00:12:57,180
You think I see Chloe
as a replacement for Jin Ju?

160
00:12:58,880 --> 00:13:00,250
Is that what this is about again?

161
00:13:00,550 --> 00:13:01,550
I don't know.

162
00:13:03,250 --> 00:13:05,520
What exactly am I trying to say?

163
00:13:07,220 --> 00:13:09,190
Let me make one thing
perfectly clear.

164
00:13:10,690 --> 00:13:13,230
I've never seen Chloe
as a replacement for Jin Ju.

165
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:16,430
My feelings for Chloe
and my feelings for Jin Ju...

166
00:13:17,740 --> 00:13:18,840
are completely different.

167
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:24,940
Your feelings for Chloe?

168
00:13:26,140 --> 00:13:29,080
You're actually saying that
after I told you I liked her?

169
00:13:29,350 --> 00:13:31,720
We still don't know how she feels.

170
00:13:41,730 --> 00:13:43,230
If that's how you're going to be,

171
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:46,160
it makes me want to play dirty.

172
00:13:48,870 --> 00:13:52,970
Now I don't even want to tell you
Chloe is really Baek Jin Ju.

173
00:13:55,810 --> 00:13:58,010
If you're going to be selfish,
then...

174
00:14:00,380 --> 00:14:02,210
I can be selfish too, right?

175
00:14:11,190 --> 00:14:13,620
So you're over the woman who died?

176
00:14:13,820 --> 00:14:15,360
If I were her,

177
00:14:16,090 --> 00:14:18,200
I would've told you to stay
in the past.

178
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:22,570
Not to move on so easily.

179
00:14:24,970 --> 00:14:26,300
Just stay right where you are.

180
00:14:31,040 --> 00:14:32,540
The Jin Ju I knew...

181
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:35,150
wouldn't keep me tied to the past.

182
00:14:37,250 --> 00:14:39,180
And from what I've learned
about you,

183
00:14:39,680 --> 00:14:41,950
you wouldn't think that either.

184
00:14:43,920 --> 00:14:45,490
So why did you say that?

185
00:15:05,540 --> 00:15:07,880
What do you mean Park Hyun Jun
suspects who you really are?

186
00:15:08,010 --> 00:15:09,410
What happened between you two?

187
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:11,820
He asked to meet.
I thought it was about our wedding,

188
00:15:11,880 --> 00:15:14,020
but he tested me
with a chestnut cake.

189
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:15,390
A chestnut cake?

190
00:15:16,020 --> 00:15:17,790
To see if you're allergic?

191
00:15:18,290 --> 00:15:19,520
I think so.

192
00:15:19,620 --> 00:15:22,790
But Min Jun's the only one
who knows about my allergy.

193
00:15:23,330 --> 00:15:24,900
Maybe Min Jun told him.

194
00:15:25,430 --> 00:15:27,500
He could've already figured it out.

195
00:15:28,530 --> 00:15:30,730
We don't know yet.

196
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:34,870
Hyun Jun may try to confirm
his suspicions through you,

197
00:15:35,270 --> 00:15:36,840
so be careful not to give me away.

198
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:38,380
To be safe,
we can't take any chances.

199
00:15:38,780 --> 00:15:42,380
You must avoid Park Hyun Jun
and withdraw the proposal.

200
00:15:42,450 --> 00:15:43,450
No.

201
00:15:43,950 --> 00:15:46,350
If I back off now,
he'll get even more suspicious.

202
00:15:46,350 --> 00:15:47,380
Jin Ju!

203
00:15:47,380 --> 00:15:49,590
If I were going to run away
every time things got dangerous,

204
00:15:51,060 --> 00:15:52,890
I never would've come back
in the first place.

205
00:15:55,530 --> 00:15:58,330
And I need this marriage.

206
00:15:58,360 --> 00:16:00,730
You'll end up ruining
your entire life.

207
00:16:00,730 --> 00:16:02,430
And what if I give up now?

208
00:16:03,700 --> 00:16:07,970
Either way, my revenge and my life
will be ruined.

209
00:16:10,610 --> 00:16:12,380
Unless you're going to leave me
to do this alone,

210
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:14,850
help me.

211
00:16:31,200 --> 00:16:32,960
(Adele)

212
00:16:35,730 --> 00:16:36,970
(BIT Life, President Kim Myung Hui)

213
00:16:38,640 --> 00:16:41,540
What?
She didn't even show up for work?

214
00:16:43,310 --> 00:16:46,080
Where is she and what is she up to?

215
00:16:54,420 --> 00:16:56,750
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

216
00:17:10,130 --> 00:17:11,140
Right.

217
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:13,970
Have you confirmed
Kim Myung Hui's whereabouts?

218
00:17:14,100 --> 00:17:16,970
Yes. She was last seen
at the Adele Gallery.

219
00:17:17,840 --> 00:17:18,840
The gallery?

220
00:17:19,180 --> 00:17:21,350
After meeting with Ms. Oh,
she didn't come home...

221
00:17:21,480 --> 00:17:25,150
and only contacted her son
through Secretary Jung.

222
00:17:25,350 --> 00:17:26,520
Oh Jung Ran!

223
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:31,820
Of course she'd make her move
now that I've taken away her ledger.

224
00:17:33,620 --> 00:17:35,590
(Bion Tech)

225
00:17:35,590 --> 00:17:36,960
(BIT Life, President Kim Myung Hui)

226
00:17:39,500 --> 00:17:42,130
Do you think it's easy
holding out in this family?

227
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:45,400
How will you make her stay
if she gives up on you?

228
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:50,110
Don't you care
if you lose Mother over this?

229
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:05,490
I'm sorry for calling you
out of the blue.

230
00:18:06,420 --> 00:18:07,420
Not at all.

231
00:18:07,690 --> 00:18:11,900
Actually, we just finished
looking into your request.

232
00:18:12,430 --> 00:18:16,070
You must've wanted answers,
so go ahead and take a look.

233
00:18:28,180 --> 00:18:30,050
Something stands out, doesn't it?

234
00:18:31,520 --> 00:18:32,720
Chloe...

235
00:18:33,480 --> 00:18:37,020
While working with
a Korean environmental group,

236
00:18:37,220 --> 00:18:40,290
she disappeared
on a snow-covered mountain.

237
00:18:41,160 --> 00:18:43,130
They searched for a week,

238
00:18:43,590 --> 00:18:45,160
but never found her.

239
00:18:45,530 --> 00:18:48,670
So, are you saying Chloe died?

240
00:18:48,730 --> 00:18:52,470
You could say she came back
from the dead.

241
00:18:53,600 --> 00:18:56,740
She was found near a river,
far from the snow-covered mountain...

242
00:18:56,940 --> 00:18:59,140
where she disappeared.

243
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:02,450
Since she had crossed the border
and was unconscious,

244
00:19:02,450 --> 00:19:05,380
it took them a while
to identify her.

245
00:19:05,950 --> 00:19:07,650
People who don't know
the whole story...

246
00:19:08,020 --> 00:19:09,050
think...

247
00:19:09,550 --> 00:19:11,020
Chloe died.

248
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:16,090
She was missing for about a month
before she was found.

249
00:19:17,930 --> 00:19:21,730
Are you sure she survived
after going missing?

250
00:19:23,170 --> 00:19:25,770
The records from that time
confirm it.

251
00:19:27,470 --> 00:19:31,310
So Chloe and Baek Jin Ju
are two different people after all.

252
00:19:33,280 --> 00:19:34,810
I knew it was impossible,

253
00:19:36,210 --> 00:19:38,850
but I prayed
that she was somehow still alive.

254
00:19:40,820 --> 00:19:43,890
So in the end, even Baek Jin Ju...

255
00:19:45,520 --> 00:19:48,690
Even the girl Min Jun loved
died at Park Tae Ho's hands.

256
00:19:50,430 --> 00:19:53,000
How could he do something so cruel
to Min Jun?

257
00:19:59,100 --> 00:20:02,610
I'm sorry,
but may I ask for one more favor?

258
00:20:03,670 --> 00:20:05,080
Go ahead.

259
00:20:05,740 --> 00:20:06,740
Park Tae Ho.

260
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:10,380
Please look into Chairman Park
of the Adele Group.

261
00:20:13,150 --> 00:20:14,180
Excuse me?

262
00:20:14,820 --> 00:20:16,420
Being close to him,

263
00:20:17,020 --> 00:20:18,990
I thought I knew him
better than anyone,

264
00:20:19,690 --> 00:20:21,430
but it turns out
I know nothing at all.

265
00:20:22,360 --> 00:20:23,490
Please.

266
00:20:31,540 --> 00:20:33,340
Kim Myung Hui stayed out all night?

267
00:20:36,070 --> 00:20:38,610
Her clothes are still here,
so I don't think she ran away.

268
00:20:38,910 --> 00:20:41,350
We didn't know
because we were in the annex,

269
00:20:41,350 --> 00:20:42,750
but President Kim stayed out,

270
00:20:42,810 --> 00:20:46,020
and I heard Chairman Park
was furious.

271
00:20:46,120 --> 00:20:48,590
On top of that,
she didn't even show up for work.

272
00:20:49,790 --> 00:20:52,760
Why is she acting unlike herself?
It's making me anxious.

273
00:20:53,890 --> 00:20:55,230
What's there to be anxious about?

274
00:20:57,260 --> 00:20:59,900
She was talking nonsense
about taking over my life.

275
00:21:00,130 --> 00:21:01,330
What do you think she meant?

276
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:03,730
Why would she want to live as you?

277
00:21:04,170 --> 00:21:05,540
Your life isn't that great.

278
00:21:05,800 --> 00:21:06,800
What?

279
00:21:07,340 --> 00:21:08,540
What's so bad about my life?

280
00:21:08,540 --> 00:21:10,370
At least President Kim...

281
00:21:12,440 --> 00:21:15,750
isn't being abused by Chairman Park.

282
00:21:17,650 --> 00:21:21,790
What's so great about having to walk
on eggshells around Chairman Park?

283
00:21:22,120 --> 00:21:23,120
I'm just worried...

284
00:21:23,350 --> 00:21:27,690
he'll take it out on you
for her not coming home.

285
00:21:28,230 --> 00:21:29,260
Why me?

286
00:21:29,390 --> 00:21:32,430
She chose not to come home
after meeting you.

287
00:21:32,560 --> 00:21:35,630
What if Chairman Park
blames you for it?

288
00:21:37,600 --> 00:21:41,040
Kim Myung Hui, that sly fox.
Did she set me up again?

289
00:21:41,510 --> 00:21:42,570
Oh Jung Ran!

290
00:21:57,050 --> 00:22:00,120
What did you do
to Myung Hui this time?

291
00:22:02,030 --> 00:22:03,230
What do you mean?

292
00:22:03,290 --> 00:22:06,300
Of course.
There's no way you'd just confess.

293
00:22:06,800 --> 00:22:07,860
Manager Kang!

294
00:22:13,740 --> 00:22:15,510
Good grief.

295
00:22:16,170 --> 00:22:17,640
(Gallery Director, Oh Jung Ran)

296
00:22:18,710 --> 00:22:19,710
Honey.

297
00:22:20,440 --> 00:22:23,510
I was cutting you some slack
because of an important deal,

298
00:22:23,780 --> 00:22:25,550
but you just had to cause trouble.

299
00:22:25,750 --> 00:22:29,150
As of today,
you're done with the gallery.

300
00:22:32,360 --> 00:22:34,390
Is this about the ledger entry
for Eunhwa Trading,

301
00:22:35,360 --> 00:22:37,690
or because Kim Myung Hui
didn't come home?

302
00:22:37,860 --> 00:22:40,000
No matter how badly she was treated,

303
00:22:40,800 --> 00:22:42,770
she would grit her teeth and endure.

304
00:22:42,930 --> 00:22:46,000
So for someone like that
to back down like this?

305
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:50,140
It means this was more
than just you blowing off steam.

306
00:22:50,770 --> 00:22:53,140
If you want your job back
at the gallery,

307
00:22:53,310 --> 00:22:56,610
you'd better tell me exactly
what happened.

308
00:23:03,790 --> 00:23:06,760
In the end, all you care about
is that tramp, Kim Myung Hui.

309
00:23:07,020 --> 00:23:10,230
Stop changing the subject
and answer me.

310
00:23:11,360 --> 00:23:12,800
I hate to break it to you,

311
00:23:14,030 --> 00:23:16,930
but Kim Myung Hui
will never be yours.

312
00:23:18,070 --> 00:23:19,070
Right.

313
00:23:19,740 --> 00:23:21,940
Perhaps that's all I need.

314
00:23:24,370 --> 00:23:25,580
You're laughing?

315
00:23:26,640 --> 00:23:27,740
The gallery?

316
00:23:28,350 --> 00:23:30,310
You think you can just
take it away like that?

317
00:23:31,380 --> 00:23:33,520
If I walk away,
won't you be the one in a bind?

318
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:36,290
What about that important business
you mentioned?

319
00:23:37,750 --> 00:23:40,690
Go ahead.
See how well you manage without me.

320
00:23:41,320 --> 00:23:45,530
It's time you learned the hard way
just how crucial I am to you.

321
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:49,830
What? Why you... Of all the nerve!

322
00:23:51,030 --> 00:23:52,140
Unbelievable.

323
00:23:52,870 --> 00:23:55,410
Because of her,
even Myung Hui dared to...

324
00:23:57,940 --> 00:24:00,740
I can't believe
she caused all this drama...

325
00:24:00,740 --> 00:24:02,310
with such a major deal at stake.

326
00:24:04,150 --> 00:24:06,980
Manager Kang,
you'll handle the exhibition deal.

327
00:24:07,780 --> 00:24:10,690
Also, find Kim Myung Hui
and bring her to me!

328
00:24:11,120 --> 00:24:12,120
Yes, sir.

329
00:24:15,290 --> 00:24:16,290
Darn it.

330
00:24:20,130 --> 00:24:22,200
(The late Baek Jun Gi,
The late Baek Jin Ju)

331
00:24:48,390 --> 00:24:49,590
Dr. Baek.

332
00:24:51,230 --> 00:24:53,130
I'm sorry I haven't been by sooner.

333
00:24:53,260 --> 00:24:54,630
(The late Baek Jun Gi,
The late Baek Jin Ju)

334
00:24:54,630 --> 00:24:57,670
I'm so sorry it took me this long.

335
00:25:02,170 --> 00:25:03,170
And...

336
00:25:13,720 --> 00:25:14,920
I apologize...

337
00:25:16,050 --> 00:25:17,150
again.

338
00:25:20,820 --> 00:25:21,830
I...

339
00:25:23,230 --> 00:25:25,330
Even though I know
what Park Tae Ho did,

340
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:28,500
I've decided to look the other way.

341
00:25:35,410 --> 00:25:37,310
I know I'm being a coward,

342
00:25:40,380 --> 00:25:41,610
but please forgive me.

343
00:26:14,740 --> 00:26:15,980
How are things?

344
00:26:17,410 --> 00:26:19,950
Chairman Park forced Oh Jung Ran
out of the gallery.

345
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:22,290
And he has Manager Kang looking
for you.

346
00:26:22,650 --> 00:26:23,650
Oh Jung Ran.

347
00:26:24,820 --> 00:26:26,560
Was she only kicked out
of the gallery?

348
00:26:27,190 --> 00:26:30,290
Yes. He didn't kick her
out of the house.

349
00:26:30,660 --> 00:26:33,360
Chairman Park must have grilled her
about what happened,

350
00:26:34,530 --> 00:26:37,700
but she must not have told him
she revealed the secret to me.

351
00:26:40,140 --> 00:26:42,370
It's not like telling him
would help her.

352
00:26:44,810 --> 00:26:45,910
In that case,

353
00:26:47,280 --> 00:26:48,880
it's time for me
to meet Park Tae Ho.

354
00:26:52,750 --> 00:26:54,050
(Consultant, Chloe Lee)

355
00:26:56,390 --> 00:26:59,560
(Team Leader, Choi Yu Na)

356
00:27:04,590 --> 00:27:07,600
Shouldn't I tell the chairman
and get rid of her?

357
00:27:09,670 --> 00:27:10,670
That's a bad idea.

358
00:27:11,100 --> 00:27:13,100
What if it backfires
and she goes to Min Jun...

359
00:27:13,540 --> 00:27:15,040
and ruins my wedding?

360
00:27:17,240 --> 00:27:20,580
Then again, just trusting her
and waiting is risky too.

361
00:27:23,150 --> 00:27:24,150
Chloe.

362
00:27:24,850 --> 00:27:27,080
How are you going to prove
you're on my side?

363
00:27:33,360 --> 00:27:35,260
What is it? Are you here to see me?

364
00:27:37,930 --> 00:27:39,100
Can we talk for a minute?

365
00:27:40,600 --> 00:27:41,970
What could the two of you
have to talk about?

366
00:27:43,100 --> 00:27:44,670
Whatever you have to say,
say it here.

367
00:27:46,270 --> 00:27:47,540
This is between the two of us.

368
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:49,010
What?

369
00:27:49,540 --> 00:27:50,710
The two of you?

370
00:27:57,550 --> 00:27:58,550
Ms. Lee.

371
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:01,720
You're giving me
the wrong idea here.

372
00:28:02,550 --> 00:28:05,760
I thought you said
you'd help us get married.

373
00:28:07,960 --> 00:28:11,390
She turned "I won't get in the way"
into "I'll help?"

374
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:14,800
Why don't you tell us right here
how you're going to help?

375
00:28:15,730 --> 00:28:18,900
Right in front of Min Jun.

376
00:28:30,150 --> 00:28:32,280
How Baek Jin Ju is still alive...

377
00:28:33,880 --> 00:28:35,820
and why she returned as Chloe.

378
00:28:38,150 --> 00:28:39,190
Should I be looking into this?

379
00:28:41,860 --> 00:28:44,190
And if it turns out
she's really Baek Jin Ju, then I...

380
00:28:50,930 --> 00:28:52,670
If Min Jun were in my place,

381
00:28:54,770 --> 00:28:56,870
he wouldn't have been such a coward.

382
00:29:01,040 --> 00:29:02,250
If it were him,

383
00:29:04,310 --> 00:29:05,750
no matter how much he wanted her...

384
00:29:14,360 --> 00:29:15,860
Is what Choi Yu Na said true?

385
00:29:16,360 --> 00:29:18,830
Did you say you'd help her marry me?

386
00:29:23,230 --> 00:29:24,230
I did.

387
00:29:24,830 --> 00:29:27,700
I'm going to help
the two of you get married.

388
00:29:32,580 --> 00:29:35,310
Did you forget what you told me?

389
00:29:36,110 --> 00:29:39,350
It wasn't that long ago you told me
not to run away like a coward...

390
00:29:39,450 --> 00:29:41,350
and to take control of my life.

391
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:45,160
But now you're going
to help her marry me?

392
00:29:47,260 --> 00:29:50,090
When you know how badly
I want out of this marriage?

393
00:29:50,260 --> 00:29:52,700
How could you,
when you know who I really want?

394
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:56,430
What's that supposed to mean?

395
00:29:57,600 --> 00:29:58,670
Are you saying...

396
00:29:59,740 --> 00:30:02,370
you actually confessed your feelings
to Chloe?

397
00:30:03,540 --> 00:30:04,540
Is this because of me?

398
00:30:05,310 --> 00:30:07,910
Are you running away because my feelings
make you uncomfortable?

399
00:30:08,080 --> 00:30:10,450
Is this your response to how I feel?

400
00:30:10,450 --> 00:30:11,480
That's enough!

401
00:30:21,120 --> 00:30:22,430
A response to how you feel?

402
00:30:23,930 --> 00:30:25,730
That's something I should answer,
not Chloe.

403
00:30:27,300 --> 00:30:28,300
What?

404
00:30:35,940 --> 00:30:37,170
Fine.

405
00:30:39,180 --> 00:30:40,210
Do whatever you want.

406
00:30:43,880 --> 00:30:44,880
Let's...

407
00:30:46,520 --> 00:30:47,550
get married.

408
00:31:22,120 --> 00:31:23,120
Kim Myung Hui?

409
00:31:54,080 --> 00:31:55,750
What's going on here?

410
00:31:57,550 --> 00:32:00,790
I wanted to show you
how I really feel, sir.

411
00:32:02,330 --> 00:32:03,330
How you feel?

412
00:32:07,960 --> 00:32:09,600
If you want to know how I feel,

413
00:32:10,230 --> 00:32:12,000
give me the gallery.

414
00:32:13,540 --> 00:32:14,670
The gallery?

415
00:32:44,630 --> 00:32:47,670
(Pearl in Red)

416
00:32:47,940 --> 00:32:51,210
The pure, noble Kim Myung Hui
is dead and gone.

417
00:32:51,610 --> 00:32:54,710
Instead of living in misery,
I'm going to take what I want.

418
00:32:55,080 --> 00:32:57,280
Something's not right.
She's a completely different person.

419
00:32:57,280 --> 00:33:00,080
She wasn't like that,
even when she first moved in.

420
00:33:00,220 --> 00:33:01,220
That's absurd.

421
00:33:01,220 --> 00:33:04,150
No one changes that drastically
overnight.

422
00:33:04,290 --> 00:33:06,690
How did you get in here?

423
00:33:06,690 --> 00:33:09,760
Were you playing me from the start,
like this was all part of some plan?

424
00:33:09,760 --> 00:33:10,830
Who the heck are you?

425
00:33:11,060 --> 00:33:12,360
Who are you? Tell me!

426
00:33:13,560 --> 00:33:15,570
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
